Talking to people with LWOP sentences put some sense in my head. I have since walked away from said gang and work at a nonprofit helping people get housing off the streets. I still don't think I'm giving back enough.

It haunts me. I have done some terrible stuff on the yard enforcng rules doing "removals" which is the act of beating someone near to death and even stabbing sex offenders. I have witnessed people killed multiple times. I should have done less time, but these acts gave me more time.

I can't seem to shake it. I walk around in public like a hard ass and am always ready for combat looking over my shoulder. My partner makes fun of me for wearing clothes to bed to be ready. I work out religiously. I just can't stop replaying it. I never smile and hardly laugh.

A good deal of my fear is running into the gang I dropped out of as well. I'm also a little weird from so much isolation in the SHU. 

I have been to several doctors and done a ton of mindfulness with no help. Guess I'm a lost soul.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/B3MTELV</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MegatronTheDecepticon]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>he can float here all day</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/jNw4GVK</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6VBq2yd.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/jNw4GVK</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SilkyHill]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The best boi :D</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/lP0btkl</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kZJZCgU.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Source:  https://www.instagram.com/reel/C-QLuGyPZ5e/</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/lP0btkl</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Rammsteinstochter]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Thursday unhinged meme dump of pure chaos #253 (hang in there, weekend is coming soon)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/almB2LW</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/H1RoIQm.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>1</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CB93bqq.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>2. MRW my boss tells me that there has been a sick call on the late shift...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Bao7PD5.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>3. How do I be as smooth as this guy? Send tutorials please</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ilR1whf.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>4. LANGUAGE</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/A1Yh3NY.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>5. Cat getting b